{"word":"G2112 - εὐθέως - euthéōs - yoo-theh'-oce - Anon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐθέως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euthéōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-theh'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Anon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உடனே, சீக்கிரமாய், முன்னே - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"straightway, immediately, forthwith"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G2117 - εὐθύς - euthýs - yoo-thoos'/2117\">G2117</a>; <i>directly</i>, that is, <i>at once</i> or <i>soon:</i> - anon, as soon as, forthwith, immediately, shortly, straightway.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}